title: Doctor Who Season 1-7
description:
Rehosted as previous one stopped being seedable on my computer.

I found the first 5 seasons and several of the specials compiled and uploaded by another uploader. I also found season 6 and 7 uploaded by others. I individually downloaded other specials and added them all together into one file.

Credit to the uploaders who put up the individual pieces of this.		


Uploaded and compiled by Morihiroshi.


Hope you enjoy this upload. The readme contains some basic information to watching the specials and movies in the correct order.		

This upload contains almost every video of the new series and is up to date as of 11/13
